N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 21 ยง 1274.13 - Vehicles subject to detention for nonpayment of parking charges

State Regulations

The manager shall have authority to detain vehicles
parked in air terminal vehicular parking areas for non-payment of parking
charges. Notes
